# LFP Accounting — pull every 15 minutes
# Install with: crontab -e   (then paste this line)
# Cron is started automatically by the Pi at boot, so this survives reboots.
#
# This is the ACTIVE mechanism on the production Pi (the systemd unit/timer
# in this folder are an unused alternative). Adjust the path, --printer IP,
# and interval to match your install.
#
# pull.log is gitignored and grows over time; to cap it, rotate with logrotate
# or periodically truncate (e.g. a weekly `: > pull.log` cron entry).

*/15 * * * * cd /home/gbgbild/gbgbild-accounting && /usr/bin/python3 lfp_accounting.py --printer 192.168.1.55 pull >> /home/gbgbild/gbgbild-accounting/pull.log 2>&1
